    "Regulatory lag.",
    "Traditional lawmaking mechanisms based on hierarchical and procedurally burdened rulemaking models show inertia and inability to respond quickly to technological innovations.",
    "Such regulatory inertia complicates law enforcement and creates situations of legal uncertainty.4.",
    "Fragmented regulatory framework.",
    "The lack of coherence between different sectoral and industry-specific acts regulating digital relations causes fragmentation of the legal space, legal conflicts and a decrease in the effectiveness of legal influence."
